From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|lang=fro|designer}} < {{etyl|la}} {{term|lang=la|designare||to mark out, point out, describe, design, contrive}} < {{term|de-}} (or {{term|dis-}}) + {{term|lang=la|signare||to mark}} < {{term|lang=la|signum||mark}}.

